OL,4,C'should be UK-wide'
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's justice minister
OL,7,Fsays legislation to clear the names of
OL,8,Fsub-postmasters wronged in the Horizon
OL,9,Fscandal should apply UK-wide.
OL,11,FNaomi Long was speaking after the
OL,12,FGovernment issued a statement .
OL,14,FShe said she is "incredibly
OL,15,Fdisappointed" that the law, expected
OL,16,Fto come into effect by the end of
OL,17,FJuly, won't cover Northern Ireland.
OL,19,FMs Long said her department is now
OL,20,F"urgently" reviewing options.
