OL,6,FMeanwhile solicitors representing
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland sub-postmasters say
OL,8,Fthe Government's announcement that
OL,9,Flegislation to overturn convictions
OL,10,Fwill only apply to England and Wales
OL,11,Fhas created "real concern" for sub-
OL,12,Fpostmasters here.
OL,14,FMadden and Finucane have written to
OL,15,Fthe Executive seeking "urgent
OL,16,Fclarification" on the matter.
OL,18,F"Today's announcement means that there
OL,19,Fis uncertainty as to how and when
OL,20,Flegislation will be introduced in NI,"
OL,21,Fa statement said.
