OL,6,F"Unfortunately, this uncertainty has
OL,7,Fadded to the ongoing distress suffered
OL,8,Fby wrongly convicted subpostmasters in
OL,9,FNI and means that they could be left
OL,10,Fin a worse position that those in
OL,11,FEngland and Wales.
OL,13,F"I have written to the NI Executive to
OL,14,Fseek urgent clarification regarding
OL,15,Ftheir response to today's
OL,16,Fannouncement."
OL,18,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak announced
OL,19,Fin January the Government would
OL,20,Fintroduce a new law to quash victims'
OL,21,Fconvictions.
