OL,6,FIt comes after the ITV drama led to
OL,7,Ffresh scrutiny on the Post Office and
OL,8,Fthe government over the scandal.
OL,10,FOn Thursday Post Office minister Kevin
OL,11,FHollinrake issued a statement
OL,12,Fdetailing the criteria under which
OL,13,Fvictims can have their convictions
OL,14,Fquashed, they include:
OL,16,FMr Hollinrake said: "The legislation,
OL,17,Fwhich will be brought forward shortly,
OL,18,Fwill quash all convictions which are
OL,19,Fidentified as being in scope.
