OL,6,F"That scope will be defined by a set
OL,7,Fof clear and objective criteria which
OL,8,Fwill be set out in the legislation and
OL,9,Fwill not require any element of
OL,10,Fdiscretion or subjective analysis in
OL,11,Forder to be applied."
OL,13,FMore than 700 branch managers were
OL,14,Fprosecuted by the Post Office between
OL,15,F1999 and 2015 after faulty Horizon
OL,16,Faccounting software made it look as
OL,17,Fthough money was missing from their
OL,18,Fshops.
